629
00:29:52,250 --> 00:29:53,850
You're destined to be alone.

630
00:30:05,980 --> 00:30:07,110
Don't be this stupid

631
00:30:07,940 --> 00:30:08,740
in the future.

632
00:30:10,940 --> 00:30:11,870
I have no choice.

633
00:30:12,260 --> 00:30:14,020
Fools always do stupid things.

634
00:30:14,500 --> 00:30:15,630
I will never change.

635
00:30:18,730 --> 00:30:19,770
When you go out,

636
00:30:20,260 --> 00:30:21,420
