639
00:30:25,300 --> 00:30:25,780
You...

640
00:30:31,260 --> 00:30:32,540
Unreasonable.

641
00:30:33,060 --> 00:30:34,220
Unbelievable.

642
00:30:38,460 --> 00:30:39,420
Mr. Ji.

643
00:30:39,900 --> 00:30:42,020
