695
00:32:38,020 --> 00:32:39,150
It's different now.

696
00:32:39,340 --> 00:32:40,300
What's the difference?

697
00:32:40,300 --> 00:32:41,560
You two are different.

698
00:32:42,460 --> 00:32:43,180
So,

699
00:32:43,700 --> 00:32:46,900
