700
00:32:47,500 --> 00:32:48,500
No.

701
00:32:49,020 --> 00:32:50,020
It's embarrassing.

702
00:32:50,020 --> 00:32:51,060
Lady,

703
00:32:51,500 --> 00:32:53,220
